# ── Frontend (Vite) ──────────────────────────────────────
#
# This file is a TEMPLATE. Copy it to .env (local dev),
# .env.staging, or .env.production and fill in real values.
# Those real files are git-ignored and stay on each machine.
#
# VITE_API_URL
#   Leave EMPTY for local dev (Vite proxy handles /api & /socket.io).
#   Set to the server address for deployed builds.
#   Local dev:  (empty)
#   Staging:    (empty — or the staging server URL if not localhost)
#   Production: http://129.212.199.25
VITE_API_URL=

# VITE_APP_LABEL
#   Normally auto-detected from the git branch name by vite.config.ts:
#     main            → (empty)  = production
#     staging         → Staging
#     features/xyz    → xyz
#   Set explicitly only if you need to override.
# VITE_APP_LABEL=